step:
1: download languages xpi files example
wget -r ftp://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/firefox/releases/17.0.1/linux-i686/xpi/

2: open xpi files with ark

3: give the command

for j in * ; do mv "$j" "langpack-$j@firefox.mozilla.org"; done

4: drop the files to langpack-ff

5: drop the searchplugins files in to :  langpack-ff/langpack-ach@firefox.mozilla.org/chrome/ach/locale/browser/

https://github.com/circass/elemantary-icon/tree/master/ff-langpack-searchplugins

6: tar cJvf firefox-l10n-18.0.2.tar.xz --exclude=.hgtags --exclude=.hgignore --exclude=.hg langpack-ff